title: The FBI Strikes Again! (Ep 1841)
description:
In this episode, I address the latest explosive revelations about FBI corruption and the targeting of Donald Trump. 

News Picks:

FBI special agent who opened Trump investigation reportedly escorted out of Bureau headquarters.

The Ministry of Truth is back?


A detailed analysis of the government’s efforts to censor free speech via “disinformation.”


Joe Biden picks Hunter laptop denier for presidential intelligence board.


Here’s the link to the “Transition Integrity Project” paper calling for a “street fight.”

Before FBI seized privileged Trump memos, DOJ filter teams already tainted by legal controversy.


The Biden White House hits a new low with the student loan disaster. 

For Many Americans, Cancel Culture is Self-Inflicted.
